.Sh NAME
.Nm ow
.Nd Dallas Semiconductor 1-Wire bus
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd device ow
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
module implements the Dallas Semiconductor 1-Wire bus.
It attaches to the
.Xr owc 4
driver, which implements the low-level signaling of the
1-Wire bus.
